    <div class="about-text">
      <p class="section-tag">About Me</p>
      <h2 class="section-title">I Build Systems That <em>Work For You</em></h2>
      <p>My name is Ruth Ogohi and I am a Virtual Assistant based in Abuja, Nigeria. I specialize in Operations and Organization — which simply means I help businesses run better by creating structure where there is none.</p>
      <p>I do not just complete tasks and move on. I look at the bigger picture, identify what is slowing you down and build solutions that keep working long after I am done. Think of me as the person who keeps everything running behind the scenes.</p>
