      <p class="service-desc">Going on a business trip? I handle everything — flights, hotels, visas, local transport and day by day schedules. All researched properly so you can focus on your meetings, not the logistics.</p>
    </div>
    <div class="service-card">
      <span class="service-icon">📋</span>
      <h3 class="service-name">Administrative Support</h3>
      <p class="service-desc">Scheduling, email management, research, data entry, meeting notes — the everyday tasks that eat up your time. I handle them so you can focus on the work only you can do.</p>
    </div>
    <div class="service-card">
      <span class="service-icon">🔄</span>
      <h3 class="service-name">QA Documentation</h3>
